## Limitations
The report is based on available online resources and may not cover all possible areas of improvement due to the dynamic nature of workplace environments. Additionally, the findings are limited to the perspectives and data provided by the sources reviewed, which may not fully represent all industries or organizational contexts. Further research and tailored assessments may be necessary for specific organizational needs.